column2: "Your expression says you went to a new place again."
"The Dragonkin country on Amduscia? A floating continent in the sky? I can't even imagine it."
"And there are dragons the larger than us? Wow, the scale must be entirely different there."
"If it's in the sky, is the wind strong? You can't fall off can you? Are you really okay there?"
"If you suddenly get blown off by the wind then what happens?"
"But still, being up in the sky, that sounds nice."
"Some day, I would like to go see it."
